{"tid":1473401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國及歐盟密切關注香港示威活動","createTime":"2019-08-14T23:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:23:01.000Z","uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e78fb3dc5131162c6e48795e44d4b4d4a2d876c2","tid":1473401,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:43:13.000Z","msg":"美國國務院發言人表示, 十分關注有報道指, 有大批武警集結在鄰近香港邊境的深圳, 又呼籲各方克制, 不要使用暴力. <br />\n     美聯社報導, 衛星照片顯示有數百輛中國武警部隊的裝甲運兵車,和其他車輛停在深圳的體育場.<br />\n    美國國務院發言人又指, 香港政府需要尊重市民的言論及集會自由, 並強調持續削減香港高度自治, 會影響香港的國際地位.<br />\n    而法國外長勒德里昂呼籲, 香港政府重新與示威者對話, 和平解決現時的社會危機.勒德里昂在聲明指, 基本法及一國兩制,確保香港安定繁榮, 亦都保障人權, 高度自治及法治, 強調法國及歐盟, 會密切關注香港的示威活動.德國總理默克爾呼籲, 用盡一切方法避免暴力, 在對話的框架下尋求解決方案的可能性."},{"pid":"c6b4a4bcc2c4e88099eaa35a4870fce29cf027fc","tid":1473401,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:46:31.000Z","msg":"最好派觀察員、醫療隊黎啦<br />\n唔好再得把口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b52c71b4fc7822291dee725cc57a4c6cf2676de","tid":1473401,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:23:01.000Z","msg":"[816]請參加英美港民，主權在民集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQj6qXg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQj6qXg.png&h=e0f826c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRhcmvC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRhcmvC.png&h=19abb5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38FJtaD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38FJtaD.png&h=503acc82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ghVmeQD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FghVmeQD.png&h=22f5e2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割！我哋一定會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}